---
description: Keep gql documents out of View files in web/app
globs: web/app/src/**/*.ts,web/app/src/**/*.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---

# Frontend GraphQL Document Placement

- GraphQL operation documents live only in `web/app/src/Graphql/Operations/Gql/`. Never place `gql` template blocks in View/UI files.
- Views import the generated typed hooks (from codegen) — run `npm run codegen` after adding operations.
- Import `@base/design-system` and `@base/core` from their package roots only; no deep `src/` imports across packages.
